      • fromString

        public static Tag<java.lang.String> fromString(java.lang.String tagKeyValue)
        Reverse of Tag.toString(). Parses a string of the form "key:value" into a Tag.

        If there are multiple ":" in the input string, the key will be the substring up to the first ":", and the value will be the substring after the first ":".

        Parameters:
        tagKeyValue - String of the form "key:value".
        Returns:
        Tag parsed from input.
